  "text": "Most of the presentation of the untyped part of the language is borrowed from [CITATION_1] . There, we also outline the main features of the KLAIM type system without providing the actual syntax for types, the explicit notion of run time error and the proofs of the subject reduction theorem and of the type safety theorem.",
